room_title: Escape room "Hollywood Premiere" by Escape the Mystery Room in Albany
room_address: 1 Crossgates Mall Rd Unit C107, Albany, NY 12203
room_description: As you walk down the Hollywood Walk of Fame you will see many famous celebrities. Your objective is to escape Hollywood within 50 minutes by using the clues and puzzles you will find in the room. If you make it to the Oscars, don't forget to thank us in your speech.
